{"comments":"Phone number formatting engine.\n\nProvides format-as-you-type functionality with cursor position preservation.\nThis is pure data transformation — no side effects, no FFI.\n\n## Key Features\n\n- Format phone numbers according to country patterns\n- Preserve cursor position through format changes\n- Support partial formatting during input\n- Calculate cursor position after formatting\n\n## Format Pattern Syntax\n\n- `#` = digit placeholder\n- Any other character = literal (inserted as-is)\n\nExamples:\n- `(###) ###-####` — US format\n- `## #### ####` — Australia format\n- `##-####-####` — Japan format\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Format a national number using the country's format pattern.\n\nExample:\n```\nformat usCountry (nationalNumber \"5551234567\")\n-- Returns: \"(555) 123-4567\"\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Phone","Country"],"Country"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Phone","NationalNumber"],"NationalNumber"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[124,46],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Phone/Format.purs","start":[124,1]},"title":"format"},{"children":[],"comments":"Format a national number with a specific pattern.\n\nReplaces `#` placeholders in the pattern with digits from the number.\nStops when either digits or placeholders run out.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"Ty